{"tid":782641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，對付大媽其實有更好方法…","createTime":"2018-08-17T01:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T02:07:40.000Z","uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b1048d69654b7b52fde2eab740df102dd7f7f7","tid":782641,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T01:59:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港法例<br />\n第400章 <br />\n《噪音管制條例》</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/095849_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F095849_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=32d081f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/095847_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F095847_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=024a74fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得1823環保署啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e42a0accef3810689d8270b07368a982cff97e00","tid":782641,"uid":136249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:03:03.000Z","msg":"差佬做唔做事又另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badf9390582a090d3947ddc12cffbd4f57cd8d1b","tid":782641,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"家農蔬果批發2分店狂播叫賣錄音　罰款1萬<br />\n<br />\n家農蔬果批發專門店有限公司2間位於油麻地新填地街及筲箕灣寶文街分店，因不斷以揚聲器持續大聲播放叫賣宣傳錄音，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有市民去年向環保署投訴</strong></span>，環保署人員於今年3及4月到2間分店調查，經評估後確認其發出噪音構成煩擾，因而提出檢控，今日(16日)在觀塘裁判法院被裁定違反《噪音管制條例》罪成，被判罰款1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n環保署發言人表示，十分關注有連鎖經營蔬菜店在多個地區的分店均涉及造成噪音煩擾，會繼續密切監察情況，嚴厲執法打擊重複違規的店鋪，除向涉案的公司提出檢控外，亦會考慮對經營涉案店鋪的公司董事提出檢控。"}]}